{
  "stem": "8370.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they have been put in the gas chamber there and finished, not to leave any witness to the job.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Why, for example, the Gestapo, the SS, have put dynamite below the old crematoriums and today, we got rubbles only?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were thinking that they destroy the evidence.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I rather see this idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's true.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Could you tell me about your experience and relationship with Colonel Boger?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, with Boger I had twice, I would say, personality clash.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One day, we worked-- it was winter-- we came back from work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was working building a road close, in the hospital area, close to the big, I would say, warehouses where worked a special kommando who selected the goods from their transport.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was different things you get, from gold to jewelry to food and clothing, and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So through the barbed wire between hospital camp and the-- the warehouse barracks, we have made some businesses, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had been every day searched, almost every day, not to bring anything in the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they throw to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we brought to the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we received some, I would say, interest, how you call it, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sometimes it was food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sometimes it was, say, for example, gold or jewelry or a watch or something like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember one day, one of my acquaintance prisoner working in the warehouse throw me, through the barbed wire, a gold coin.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had this gold coin in my hand when I walked back into the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we passed a gate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to report.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I say, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then you give the quantity of how many-- 100 [GERMAN] 100 prisoners.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we passed.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
